Name: Stasis Chamber Hallway
FirstTimeDescription: This is your first time in the hallway. It feels cold and unfamiliar.
Description: You stand in a long, featureless corridor. Dim overhead lights cast a faint, eerie glow. Rows of closed doors line both sides of the hallway.

Interactables.Name: Locked Stasis Chamber Door
Interactables.Description: Each door along the corridor appears identical, with a small rectangular window at eye level. They are all locked and sealed.
